{"tid":468262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【面目全非】乳頭瘤誤診鼻竇炎  阿婆腫瘤迫爆頭骨","createTime":"2017-11-14T08:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T09:27:08.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f55e3e66100a9716d739103fb5f893065f63ed97","tid":468262,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"圖 慎入<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510598564_4735.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510598564_4735.jpg&d=qH46E849tL3G9a%2FQy7lHyTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ea80f34b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510598564_4735.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓一名老婦鼻腔生瘤卻被誤診鼻竇炎，越醫越嚴重，腫瘤不斷生長，大得迫爆頭骨。<br />\n<br />\n71歲的伊迪莎（Editha Dadores）四年前開始感到鼻痛，醫生診斷她患鼻竇炎，給她藥物治療，但病情沒有改善。她兩年前接受手術並繼續服藥，但依然藥石無靈。<br />\n<br />\n原來，伊迪莎並非患鼻竇炎，而是生內翻性乳頭瘤（inverted papilloma）。不過，醫生發現時已經太遲，腫瘤失控增大，壓碎前頭骨，令她容顏變到認不出。<br />\n伊迪莎目前留院，醫生正等候化驗結果，以決定下一步治療方向。醫生考慮過為她進行臉部重建手術，但認為手術有一定風險。<br />\n<br />\n伊迪莎的媳婦雷娜琳（Renalyn）表示，伊迪莎接受過長期治療，但始終無法抑制腫瘤，「就像看着一宗車禍慢動作發生，卻束手無策」。雷娜琳說，伊迪莎有服藥止痛，但說話、睡眠、進食都有困難。<br />\n<br />\n有耳鼻喉專科醫生解釋，內翻性乳頭瘤多數是良性。由於瘤表面的黏膜特別脆弱，患者會經常流鼻血，甚至面部痛楚。瘤可阻塞鼻竇及鼻孔，令膿液無法流出，故可能被誤診鼻竇炎。此瘤可侵蝕鼻附近的骨骼。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》／《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171114/57455556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57455556&d=qH46E849tL3G9a%2FQy7lHyTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=faefa2a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57455556&h=8364f306\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171114/57455556</a>"},{"pid":"878acad306b09cf82d4ea7193997e7dc744b38e3","tid":468262,"uid":98232,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg&h=d4f90a5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bcdcdd84fe2f0e84dec7b462c276d3ed03df59c","tid":468262,"uid":83568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg&h=d4f90a5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33deae61e4329e97459f8adb204d5ceb0461ad78","tid":468262,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F170341_d7892bea9e4cdd7b42a791dc01aabb42.jpg&h=d4f90a5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6669e3394d92cad6a1cf61ef01405a254b210ab4","tid":4682